## 10. Indemnification

| Indemnifying Party | Scope |
|---|---|
| **AcmeCorp** | Third-party IP infringement claims arising from Services (as used per Agreement) |
| **ContosoAI** | Claims arising from ContosoAI Data, breach of Agreement, violation of law, Malicious Activity |

**Note:** AcmeCorp's IP indemnity excludes claims arising from ContosoAI's modifications, unauthorized combinations, or ContosoAI Data.

**Indemnification procedure:** Indemnitee must (a) promptly notify Indemnitor in writing, (b) grant Indemnitor sole defense/settlement control, and (c) cooperate reasonably.

