## 11. Limitation of Liability

- **Mutual exclusion** of indirect/consequential/punitive damages
- **Cap on direct damages:** 12 months of Fees paid under the applicable Order Form
- **Carve-outs** (uncapped): indemnification obligations (§11), confidentiality breaches (§9), willful misconduct/fraud, ContosoAI payment obligations, AcmeCorp incidents caused by gross negligence/willful misconduct

