## 12. Termination

| Trigger | Notice Required | Effect on Fees |
|---|---|---|
| Termination for cause (material breach) | 30 days to cure (90 days if cure is complex) | Pro-rated refund of prepaid fees |
| ContosoAI convenience termination | 90 days' written notice | No refund; all committed fees remain due |
| AcmeCorp immediate termination | Written notice | For Malicious Activity, imminent security risk, Restriction/Law breach, or 45+ days non-payment after notice |
| Force Majeure (60+ consecutive days) | Written notice | Refund of prepaid fees for post-termination period |

